      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARINERA (5) looks head and shoulders above these. Last appeared on 3 May when she led for home but found one better near the line over 1200m at Dubbo. Speedy filly who only needs to go close to that form to be taking this out. BADGERS BRIDGE (4) wasn't beaten far two back over 800m at Narromine but disappointed at Dubbo last start over today's trip. Deserves another chance. HARRY (1) has followed a similar path to BADGERS BRIDGE, with a decent effort over 800m two back at Narromine followed by a failure at Dubbo over today's journey. Should be competitive. MEGA PIXEL (2) has switched from Kris Lees to the Jane Clement stable and is fresh from a 39-day break. Placed at three of six runs so he has more talent than a lot of these. Betting holds the key. Very difficult to make a case for the others, headed by VELOCE VIXEN (8) on debut.",
